OL,6,FOwners of a dog which needed #1,200 of
OL,7,Ftreatment after being run over by an
OL,8,FAmazon delivery driver say they were
OL,9,Foffered a #25 dog bed as an apology.
OL,11,FGerman Shepherd Molly was struck by
OL,12,Fthe van in a moment caught on CCTV at
OL,13,Fthe family's home in Otley West
OL,14,FYorkshire.
OL,16,FThe footage shows the driver reversing
OL,17,Fover her and driving off without
OL,18,Fdelivering the parcel - a 20th wedding
OL,19,Fanniversary present and card.
