OL,3,CCamera catches moment courier hits dog
OL,4,Cbefore driving off
OL,6,FWhile 12-year-old Molly survived the
OL,7,Fcollision, her owner Steve Cockram,
OL,8,Fhas already spent #1,200 on surgery
OL,9,Fand could face bills of thousands of
OL,10,Fpounds for ongoing treatment.
OL,12,FThe farmer told ITV News he contacted
OL,13,FAmazon but the company failed to offer
OL,14,Fto reimburse him and offered him a new
OL,15,Fdog bed worth #25 instead.
OL,17,FMr Cockram said: "They would almost
OL,18,Fhave been better not sending that
OL,19,Fbecause it feels like an insult."
