OL,4,Cbefore driving off
OL,6,FThe driver is understood to have been
OL,7,Fworking for a courier firm employed by
OL,8,FAmazon when the incident happened in
OL,9,FSeptember.
OL,11,FMr Cockram released the CCTV after
OL,12,Fbeing angered by Amazon's response.
OL,14,F"The shock of seeing the footage and
OL,15,Feverything knitting together - you
OL,16,Fthink your heart's missed a couple of
OL,17,Fbeats," he said.
