OL,3,CCamera catches moment courier hits dog
OL,4,Cbefore driving off
OL,6,F"Fortunately, he missed her with the
OL,7,Ffront wheels. So she'd narrowly missed
OL,8,Fthe front wheels and managed to
OL,9,Fscramble out from underneath the van
OL,10,Fas he backed up.
OL,12,F"She's effectively a three-legged
OL,13,Fdog," he said. "She's managed to put a
OL,14,Flittle bit of weight on that back leg,
OL,15,Fbut it's not a great deal of use to
OL,16,Fher."
