OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F364A1763577062
OL,3,CCamera catches moment courier hits dog
OL,4,Cbefore driving off
OL,6,F"To me, that driver knew what he'd
OL,7,Fdone. Whether he intended to do it or
OL,8,Fnot is open to interpretation but once
OL,9,FMolly was underneath the van he
OL,10,Freversed up and he left at speed and
OL,11,Fdidn't deliver the parcel he came to
OL,12,Fdeliver."
OL,14,FSince the footage was posted on social
OL,15,Fmedia, Amazon has contacted Mr Cockram
OL,16,Fto say it was taking the matter
OL,17,Fseriously, but could not reimburse him
OL,18,Ffor medical fees until the family
OL,19,Fcould provide invoices.
OL,21,FAmazon has been contacted for comment.
